                <h2>Getting Started</h2>
                
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Attend the introduction session</strong> where you will receive an overview and live demonstrations</li>
                    <li><strong>Read the <a href="framework.html">6-Level Framework guide</a></strong> to understand the levels</li>
                    <li><strong>Choose your pathway</strong> based on your experience (Foundation, Development, Advanced, or Expert)</li>
                    <li><strong>Set up your tools</strong> following the <a href="resources.html">setup instructions</a></li>
                    <li><strong>Start working through modules</strong> at your own pace throughout the semester</li>
                    <li><strong>Apply your skills</strong> to real assessments and track your progress</li>
                </ol>

